    "discriminators": [
     "Cloth handling: a short multi-event scene — a grab or set-down transient wrapped in cloth rustle. Morphology is a mixture, so the tier is honest about it.",
     "Separated from MOVEMENT only by having one or two dominant transients rather than a continuous bed; the material priors are identical.",
